<div class="w3-services py-5">
    <div class="container py-lg-4">
        <div class="title-content text-left mb-lg-5 mb-4">
            <h6 class="sub-title">Our Courses</h6>
            <h3 class="hny-title">Great Courses</h3>
            <p>
                Most of our classes are in-person classes,
                provided at Garnet Valley Middle School campus on Sundays,
                to serve students in the areas neighboring Garnet Valley,
                including North Wilmington, Glen Mills, Chadds Ford, Media, West Chester, etc.
                Our in-person classes are designed in such a way that students
                can learn in a fun and interactive manner.
            </p>
            <p>
                Some of our classes are taught online. Founded in 2020, 
                when the pandemic significantly disrupted school education 
                and impaired socialization, our online courses and activities 
                during the 2020-2021 school year greatly benefited students. 
                In the future, we will carry on this tradition and provide some 
                classes virtually based on demand.
            </p>
            <p>
                We also have classes for adults, such as dance, art, and sports.
                For parents interested in taking any of the lessons,
                we believe it's a great way to learn and foster a sense of community building.
            </p>
        </div>
